<br>
While I want to go on record as saying I'd just as soon let them all rot somewhere, the entire purpose of the boycott was to make them &quot;see the light&quot; and join the rest of us in peaceful co-existance.  To that end, regardless of whether or not KGC allows Shattering Steel access I am going to allow current members of SS on all raids I run.  Not because I think they've changed, or that they feel sorry for what they've done, or what I feel sorry for them, but rather they've made the gesture we all asked of them and so we cannot do other than to accept.<br>
<br>
Now it may be that in the future SS may decide to go back to FFA or try to cause trouble in different ways.  I will deal with that then.  The future is unwritten and even George Lucas cannot see it all.  I know this isnt going to be popular, but lack of popularity never really bothered me.  Just being as fair as possible.  In this case, SS has met the requirements I set forth.  As such, they deserve to be treated as such until such time that they decide to break with KGC.  <br>
<br>
Kellory Silverstar<br>
